    {% when 'copyright' %}
      <h2>Copyright / DMCA Policy</h2>
      <p>Effective date: [Insert date]</p>
      <p>ShadabChow.com respects intellectual property rights and expects readers, contributors, sources, advertisers, and other users to do the same.</p>
      <p>This Copyright / DMCA Policy explains how copyright owners can submit copyright complaints, how the site may review takedown requests, how submitted media is handled, and how counter-notices may be processed where applicable.</p>
      <p>This page is intended to provide a clear copyright review process for a publisher site that may contain original reporting, commentary, public-interest coverage, submitted footage, images, videos, embedded media, documents, public records, screenshots, quotes, excerpts, and links.</p>
      <h3>Copyright ownership</h3>
      <p>Unless otherwise stated, original content created for ShadabChow.com is owned by ShadabChow.com or its respective author, publisher, creator, licensor, or rights holder.</p>
      <p>This may include:</p>
